        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Refundable Child Tax Credit Eligibility Verification Reform Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to require taxpayers who are claiming the refundable portion of the child tax credit to include their Social Security number on their tax return. </p>]]></text>
